[SPEAKER_02] I to je obraćanje.

544
00:26:16,559 --> 00:26:18,559
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle šta je obraćanje?

545
00:26:18,559 --> 00:26:24,559
[SPEAKER_02] Obraćanje je u stvari prezir prema životu u prijehu.

546
00:26:24,559 --> 00:26:25,559
[SPEAKER_02] Svačajući.

547
00:26:25,559 --> 00:26:26,559
[SPEAKER_02] Da je on propis.

548
00:26:26,559 --> 00:26:29,559
[SPEAKER_02] Svačajući da on nema perspektive.

549
00:26:29,559 --> 00:26:32,559
[SPEAKER_02] Svačajući da je to gubitak radosti.

550
00:26:32,559 --> 00:26:35,559
[SPEAKER_02] Svačajući da je to da poniži oče.

551
00:26:35,559 --> 00:26:39,559
[SPEAKER_02] A s druge strane postoji netko u životu u ljudi.

552
00:26:39,559 --> 00:26:42,559
[SPEAKER_02] Možda čak u času nekako promišljanja.

553
00:26:42,559 --> 00:26:44,559
[SPEAKER_02] Često se dogodi.

554
00:26:44,559 --> 00:26:48,559
[SPEAKER_02] Da čovjek još još ne veruje Bogu.

555
00:26:48,559 --> 00:26:52,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ali ovaj svijet je toliko preziraj.

556
00:26:52,559 --> 00:26:54,559
[SPEAKER_02] Da nema što izgubiti.

557
00:26:54,559 --> 00:26:57,559
[SPEAKER_02] Svijeta si jedna moja prijatelja koji je bio branitelj.

558
00:26:57,559 --> 00:26:59,559
[SPEAKER_02] malo jedni branitelj.

559
00:26:59,559 --> 00:27:01,559
[SPEAKER_02] I bio u ratu.

560
00:27:01,559 --> 00:27:03,559
[SPEAKER_02] I rat ga taj isčrpio.

561
00:27:03,559 --> 00:27:05,559
[SPEAKER_02] I nije naravno često kao i uvijek.

562
00:27:05,559 --> 00:27:07,559
[SPEAKER_02] Da nas to pomalo ide od očara.

563
00:27:07,559 --> 00:27:08,559
[SPEAKER_02] I tako dalje.

564
00:27:08,559 --> 00:27:10,559
[SPEAKER_02] I njemu se svijet rušio.

565
00:27:10,559 --> 00:27:13,559
