571
00:27:23,559 --> 00:27:25,559
[SPEAKER_02] I bio na jednoj misi.

572
00:27:25,559 --> 00:27:27,559
[SPEAKER_02] I kaže on ovako.

573
00:27:27,559 --> 00:27:29,559
