[SPEAKER_02] Super čuću.

976
00:37:12,559 --> 00:37:13,559
[SPEAKER_02] Sada ću nikada se obrati.

977
00:37:13,559 --> 00:37:14,559
[SPEAKER_02] Takav još.

978
00:37:14,559 --> 00:37:18,559
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, to je stavna je to borba.

979
00:37:18,559 --> 00:37:19,559
[SPEAKER_02] To si ja tu priznaš.

