[SPEAKER_02] "Dok kvoldeji se nikada nikada nispreča."

1095
00:39:47,559 --> 00:39:48,559
[SPEAKER_02] Meno ga upatilo.

1096
00:39:48,559 --> 00:39:51,559
[SPEAKER_02] Znaš kako sam ja papak kvoldeji se nisprečao.

1097
00:39:51,559 --> 00:39:53,559
[SPEAKER_02] I ja se isprištao.

1098
00:39:53,559 --> 00:39:54,559
[SPEAKER_02] Nekako ulazi.

1099
00:39:54,559 --> 00:39:56,559
[SPEAKER_02] Jer ne znaš nam kako bi se postao.

1100
00:39:56,559 --> 00:39:58,559
[SPEAKER_02] Misliš da dobro treba biti u tvojim princi,

1101
