[SPEAKER_02] onda to on malo mlati,

1125
00:40:44,559 --> 00:40:46,559
[SPEAKER_02] jer uvijek ima neko koji je jačiji.

1126
00:40:46,559 --> 00:40:48,559
[SPEAKER_02] A od ovek je bilo zanimljivo,

1127
00:40:48,559 --> 00:40:50,559
[SPEAKER_02] a to bi znali starija braća,

1128
00:40:50,559 --> 00:40:52,559
[SPEAKER_02] i strijučevi, i ne znam ne,

