00:54:21,559 --> 00:54:23,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sam mislio,

1599
00:54:23,559 --> 00:54:24,559
[SPEAKER_02] nakon toj temeljne opcije,

1600
00:54:24,559 --> 00:54:25,559
[SPEAKER_02] da ja sam sam gotovo,

1601
00:54:25,559 --> 00:54:26,559
[SPEAKER_02] ja sam sa to riješio,

1602
00:54:26,559 --> 00:54:28,559
[SPEAKER_02] ja sam sad našao formu,

1603
00:54:28,559 --> 00:54:29,559
[SPEAKER_02] i sad ja mogu sam,

1604
00:54:29,559 --> 00:54:30,559
[SPEAKER_02] i naravno,

1605
00:54:30,559 --> 00:54:31,559
[SPEAKER_02] to nije dobro trajalo,

1606
00:54:31,559 --> 00:54:32,559
[SPEAKER_02] dakle,

1607
00:54:32,559 --> 00:54:33,559
[SPEAKER_02] nisam slaćao dalje,

1608
00:54:33,559 --> 00:54:35,559
[SPEAKER_02] obraćenje što što se stalno događa.

1609
00:54:35,559 --> 00:54:38,559
[SPEAKER_02] Obraćenje je trajni proces.

1610
00:54:38,559 --> 00:54:41,559
[SPEAKER_02] To što se živi na ovom svijetu,

1611
00:54:41,559 --> 00:54:43,559
[SPEAKER_02] je dokaz da ti treba obraćenje.

1612
00:54:46,559 --> 00:54:49,559
[SPEAKER_02] ovo vrijeme koje ima Bog je dolga zapravo,

1613
00:54:49,559 --> 00:54:52,559
[SPEAKER_02] da treba mi još uvijek rasti u svojom bolesti,

1614
00:54:52,559 --> 00:54:53,559
[SPEAKER_02] u svojom sve.

1615
00:54:53,559 --> 00:54:55,559
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, to nešto će se trajno drugača,

1616
00:54:55,559 --> 00:54:59,559
[SPEAKER_02] nešto učem u trajno rastan,

1617
00:54:59,559 --> 00:55:00,559
[SPEAKER_02] nešto učem u...

1618
00:55:00,559 --> 00:55:03,559
[SPEAKER_02] u kojem se trajno razvijam,

1619
00:55:03,559 --> 00:55:05,559
[SPEAKER_02] i sad dakle, to vrijeme u kojem jesam,

1620
00:55:05,559 --> 00:55:07,559
[SPEAKER_02] to vrijeme moga obraćenja,

1621
00:55:07,559 --> 00:55:16,559
[SPEAKER_02] je u stvari vrijeme u kojem ja rastam u dobrojnosti,

1622
00:55:16,559 --> 00:55:18,559
[SPEAKER_02] rastam u iskustvu,

1623
00:55:18,559 --> 00:55:20,559
[SPEAKER_02] rastam u narozumivanju riječi,

1624
00:55:20,559 --> 00:55:22,559
[SPEAKER_02] rastam u molitvi.

1625
00:55:22,559 --> 00:55:25,559
[SPEAKER_02] U kojem to vrijeme u kojem osobito moleći,

1626
00:55:25,559 --> 00:55:28,559
[SPEAKER_02] dakle, zaslužujem,

1627
00:55:28,559 --> 00:55:30,559
[SPEAKER_02] sudjelujem u spasenju.

1628
00:55:30,559 --> 00:55:36,559
[SPEAKER_02] Otkrivam ne samo što je istina ili nije istina,

1629
00:55:36,559 --> 00:55:38,559
[SPEAKER_02] rastati u svojoj duhovnosti,

1630
00:55:38,559 --> 00:55:41,559
[SPEAKER_02] zapravo rastam u svojom odnosu prava crkvi,

1631
00:55:41,559 --> 00:55:46,559
[SPEAKER_02] rastam u svojom odnosu da želim služiti Kristu

1632
00:55:46,559 --> 00:55:49,559
[SPEAKER_02] i nalazim se u svojom odnosu prava Kristu.

1633
00:55:49,559 --> 00:55:53,559
[SPEAKER_02] Rastam u svojom odnosu prava crkvi.

1634
00:55:53,559 --> 00:55:56,559
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, to uvijek ima za nas puno ovaj posla,

1635
00:55:56,559 --> 00:55:59,559
[SPEAKER_02] ali dakle, to je ono što je,

1636
00:55:59,559 --> 00:56:01,559
[SPEAKER_02] dakle, nakon osobnog obraćenja,

1637
00:56:01,559 --> 00:56:03,559
[SPEAKER_02] postavljanja krijeha,

1638
00:56:03,559 --> 00:56:05,559
[SPEAKER_02] pred nama stoji taj izazov,

1639
00:56:05,559 --> 00:56:06,559
[SPEAKER_02] otkrivati u stvari,

1640
00:56:06,559 --> 00:56:08,559
[SPEAKER_02] gdje imali mjesto iz crkvi,

1641
00:56:08,559 --> 00:56:10,559
[SPEAKER_02] što li nam mogu čiti u svijetu.

1642
00:56:10,559 --> 00:56:12,559
[SPEAKER_02] i ovdje zato se ono što je uvijek.

1643
00:56:12,559 --> 00:56:13,559
[SPEAKER_02] Često se događa,

1644
00:56:13,559 --> 00:56:18,559
[SPEAKER_02] da, u zadnje vrijeme volim ovo više govoriti,

1645
00:56:18,559 --> 00:56:19,559
[SPEAKER_02] često se događa,

1646
00:56:19,559 --> 00:56:23,559
[SPEAKER_02] da mi u nekom osobnom krepostnom životu,

1647
00:56:23,559 --> 00:56:30,559
[SPEAKER_02] uz natradu je rastamo u svojom duhovnom životu,

1648
00:56:30,559 --> 00:56:32,559
[SPEAKER_02] pa rekao bih onako,

1649
00:56:32,559 --> 00:56:38,559
[SPEAKER_02] da nemamo si što puno tu prigovoriti,

1650
00:56:38,559 --> 00:56:42,559
[SPEAKER_02] ali ostaje da nekako na distanciji,

1651
00:56:42,559 --> 00:56:47,559
[SPEAKER_02] u odnosu prema ljudima i njegovim potrebama,

1652
00:56:47,559 --> 00:56:50,559
[SPEAKER_02] i u odnosu prema tome da budu slušiti.

1653
00:56:50,559 --> 00:56:52,559
[SPEAKER_02] da budu slušiti.

1654
00:56:52,559 --> 00:56:54,559
[SPEAKER_02] Vrlo je kog onih koji žive,

1655
00:56:54,559 --> 00:56:56,559
[SPEAKER_02] rekao bih, žive krepostno,

1656
00:56:56,559 --> 00:56:59,559
[SPEAKER_02] ali nisu hrabri spremni,

1657
00:56:59,559 --> 00:57:03,559
[SPEAKER_02] dok da svoj život staviti Bogu na raspolaganje,

1658
00:57:03,559 --> 00:57:06,559
[SPEAKER_02] da njihovom živom bude slušiti.

1659
00:57:06,559 --> 00:57:08,559
[SPEAKER_02] I zapravo to, rekao bih,

1660
00:57:08,559 --> 00:57:09,559
[SPEAKER_02] to svakako je,

1661
00:57:09,559 --> 00:57:10,559
[SPEAKER_02] jedan, možda ne na našem,

1662
00:57:10,559 --> 00:57:12,559
[SPEAKER_02] možda bih da tu je obraćenički život,

1663
00:57:12,559 --> 00:57:14,559
[SPEAKER_02] ali zapravo srce hoće više,

1664
00:57:14,559 --> 00:57:16,559
[SPEAKER_02] i Bog hoće više,

1665
00:57:16,559 --> 00:57:18,559
[SPEAKER_02] Isus zapobjeda, Isus želi više.

1666
00:57:18,559 --> 00:57:20,559
[SPEAKER_02] Onaj koji dolazi do toga,

1667
00:57:20,559 --> 00:57:21,559
[SPEAKER_02] da jasno,

1668
00:57:21,559 --> 00:57:22,559
[SPEAKER_02] dakle,

1669
00:57:22,559 --> 00:57:24,559
[SPEAKER_02] ajde ovako ću reći,

1670
00:57:24,559 --> 00:57:26,559
[SPEAKER_02] onaj koji dolazi do toga,

1671
00:57:26,559 --> 00:57:29,559
[SPEAKER_02] da sebi hrabro postavi pitanje.

1672
00:57:29,559 --> 00:57:32,559
[SPEAKER_02] I postavlja stalno pitanje.

1673
00:57:32,559 --> 00:57:34,559
[SPEAKER_02] Gdje me Bog treba?

1674
00:57:34,559 --> 00:57:37,559
[SPEAKER_02] Samo takav u sklari,

1675
00:57:37,559 --> 00:57:40,559
[SPEAKER_02] se nalazi na izvoru punine radosti.

1676
00:57:40,559 --> 00:57:43,559
[SPEAKER_02] Isus tako sam se ja obratio,

1677
00:57:43,559 --> 00:57:45,559
[SPEAKER_02] dakle,

1678
00:57:45,559 --> 00:57:49,559
[SPEAKER_02] ja sam bio izgubio vjeru,

1679
00:57:49,559 --> 00:57:51,559
[SPEAKER_02] to ste neki me pričao puno puta,

1680
00:57:51,559 --> 00:57:54,559
[SPEAKER_02] bio sam izgubio vjeru još u osnovnoj školi,

1681
00:57:54,559 --> 00:57:57,559
[SPEAKER_02] čak i u srednjoj školi osobi da sam bio u krizi,

1682
00:57:57,559 --> 00:57:59,559
[SPEAKER_02] i kad sam sve otratio,

1683
00:57:59,559 --> 00:58:03,559
[SPEAKER_02] bio sam na jednom seminaru koji je država imačiću splitu,

1684
00:58:03,559 --> 00:58:05,559
[SPEAKER_02] i nakon nekog vremena,

1685
00:58:05,559 --> 00:58:09,559
[SPEAKER_02] ako sam ušao jednu zajednicu malom boletvenom poslušiju,

1686
00:58:09,559 --> 00:58:13,559
[SPEAKER_02] ono mi se probudila želja za svećaničkim zvanjem,

1687
00:58:13,559 --> 00:58:16,559
[SPEAKER_02] ovdje še nam je niste pričao o svojem,

1688
00:58:16,559 --> 00:58:18,559
[SPEAKER_02] i se nekako u tom vremenu,

1689
00:58:18,559 --> 00:58:20,559
[SPEAKER_02] tako sam bio srednjoš korak,

1690
00:58:20,559 --> 00:58:22,559
[SPEAKER_02] budila se želja za svećaničkim zvanjem,

1691
00:58:22,559 --> 00:58:28,559
[SPEAKER_02] jer sam imao želju čiti nešto veliko, nešto važnije.

1692
00:58:28,559 --> 00:58:32,559
[SPEAKER_02] da nisam znao što je to.

1693
00:58:32,559 --> 00:58:37,559
[SPEAKER_02] I koliko sam nekako bio aktivan u otvorim zajednicama,

1694
00:58:37,559 --> 00:58:41,559
[SPEAKER_02] živio sakramentalno kao student i tako dalje,

1695
00:58:41,559 --> 00:58:45,559
[SPEAKER_02] tu nisam imao prazdinu u životu.

1696
00:58:45,559 --> 00:58:48,559
[SPEAKER_02] Idem na misel, molim noga,

1697
00:58:48,559 --> 00:58:53,559
[SPEAKER_02] ispovjedam se, živim pošteno,

1698
00:58:53,559 --> 00:58:56,559
[SPEAKER_01] ali sam prazan.

1699
00:58:56,559 --> 00:59:00,559
[SPEAKER_02] Nije to praznina kao ona praznina koja je bila egzistercijalna praznina,

1700
00:59:00,559 --> 00:59:03,559
[SPEAKER_02] koju sam imao, kad nisam poznao Boga,

1701
00:59:03,559 --> 00:59:04,559
[SPEAKER_02] bila sasvim drugačiji.

1702
00:59:04,559 --> 00:59:06,559
[SPEAKER_02] Mogel sam s tim živjeti,

1703
00:59:06,559 --> 00:59:08,559
[SPEAKER_02] ali,

1704
00:59:08,559 --> 00:59:11,559
[SPEAKER_02] ipak me to jako sumetalo, što se da sti.

1705
00:59:11,559 --> 00:59:14,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ta praznina, dakle, nije bila praznina bez Boga,

1706
00:59:14,559 --> 00:59:19,559
[SPEAKER_02] ne bi bila praznina zato što nisam znao gdje budu služiti.

1707
00:59:19,559 --> 00:59:24,559
[SPEAKER_02] Jeste, dakle, kao da sam se ukrstao na nekakav brod,

1708
00:59:24,559 --> 00:59:27,559
[SPEAKER_02] dakle, kao nekakvi,

1709
00:59:27,559 --> 00:59:28,559
[SPEAKER_02] kao se to kaže,

1710
00:59:28,559 --> 00:59:30,559
[SPEAKER_02] prdolovci.

1711
00:59:30,559 --> 00:59:31,559
[SPEAKER_02] Putali smo morom,

1712
00:59:31,559 --> 00:59:34,559
[SPEAKER_02] sad mi izvukao nekakav veliki brod.

1713
00:59:34,559 --> 00:59:36,559
[SPEAKER_02] Jeste se ukrstao na taj veliki brod,

1714
00:59:36,559 --> 00:59:38,559
[SPEAKER_02] i neću se udaviti.

1715
00:59:38,559 --> 00:59:40,559
[SPEAKER_02] Imam gdje spaviti.

1716
00:59:40,559 --> 00:59:43,559
[SPEAKER_02] Imam što jeste.

1717
00:59:43,559 --> 00:59:47,559
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, nema više tog straha da ćemo mora provutati.

1718
00:59:47,559 --> 00:59:49,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ali, ovo me mučilo.

1719
00:59:49,559 --> 00:59:50,559
[SPEAKER_02] Svi ako me nešto rade.

1720
00:59:50,559 --> 00:59:52,559
[SPEAKER_02] Svi imaju svoje mjesto.

1721
00:59:52,559 --> 00:59:56,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ima množstvo izazova koje ja na tom brodu mogu preuzeti.

1722
00:59:56,559 --> 00:59:58,559
[SPEAKER_02] A ne znam koje imaju mjesto.

1723
00:59:58,559 --> 01:00:05,559
[SPEAKER_02] Često, mi vijednici, dakle, tu zastanemo svoje povraćenje.

1724
01:00:05,559 --> 01:00:07,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ne možemo reći da se nismo vratili.

1725
01:00:07,559 --> 01:00:12,559
[SPEAKER_02] Jer smo živimo sakramentalno, imamo iskustvo milosti, živimo s Bogom.

1726
01:00:12,559 --> 01:00:17,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ali, često se ne usudimo, ili se ne usudimo postaviti to bitanje.

1727
01:00:17,559 --> 01:00:23,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ili ne vjerujemo da je Bog učeć, da Bog za mene sada ima nešto novo.

1728
01:00:23,559 --> 01:00:26,559
[SPEAKER_02] To je jedna noga dimenzija ne vjerujem.

1729
01:00:26,559 --> 01:00:28,559
[SPEAKER_02] Sad vjerujem da Bog postoji.

1730
01:00:28,559 --> 01:00:31,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ali ne vjerujem da on se da ima nešto novo.

1731
01:00:31,559 --> 01:00:34,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ne vjerujem da on žel da ja budem svi.

1732
01:00:34,559 --> 01:00:41,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ne vjerujem da imam svijeko poslanja i se možda bojim toga da bi me Bog mogao ugledati.

1733
01:00:41,559 --> 01:00:46,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ima jedna slika Rembrandtova obraćenje svijetoga Mateja.

1734
01:00:46,559 --> 01:00:48,559
[SPEAKER_02] Tako je to vidio.

1735
01:00:48,559 --> 01:00:49,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ali vidio je tako.

1736
01:00:49,559 --> 01:00:51,559
[SPEAKER_02] Jer često je tako vidio u život.

1737
01:00:51,559 --> 01:00:54,559
[SPEAKER_02] Isus ušao u Matejevu carinarnicu.

1738
01:00:54,559 --> 01:01:00,559
[SPEAKER_02] I on drži svoje mjenjačici, toj carinarnici.

1739
01:01:00,559 --> 01:01:04,559
[SPEAKER_02] I oborio je dogled i gledao svoje novčice.

1740
01:01:04,559 --> 01:01:05,559
[SPEAKER_02] Zašto je oborio dogled?

1741
01:01:05,559 --> 01:01:08,559
[SPEAKER_02] Da ga ne bi Isus ugledao.

1742
01:01:08,559 --> 01:01:12,559
[SPEAKER_02] I često stajemo oborio.

1743
01:01:12,559 --> 01:01:14,559
[SPEAKER_02] I to je problem.

1744
01:01:14,559 --> 01:01:17,559
[SPEAKER_02] To je problem Bogine Hradske.

1745
01:01:17,559 --> 01:01:19,559
[SPEAKER_02] To je problem i na supranitelja.

1746
01:01:19,559 --> 01:01:22,559
[SPEAKER_02] To je problem i na svećenje.

1747
01:01:22,559 --> 01:01:25,559
[SPEAKER_02] Pošao sam za Hristov.

1748
01:01:25,559 --> 01:01:28,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ostavio sam svijet.

1749
01:01:28,559 --> 01:01:34,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ali što ako Bogu pate na tome neka luda i telesa?

1750
01:01:34,559 --> 01:01:44,559
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, ili ne vjerujem da samo ima neki posebni plan i se bojim tog plana.

1751
01:01:44,559 --> 01:01:46,559
[SPEAKER_02] I ja to mi je žao gradativno.

1752
01:01:46,559 --> 01:01:53,559
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, pobožne, vjerne, dobre ljube, kojima ni navještena punina evanice.

1753
01:01:53,559 --> 01:01:55,559
[SPEAKER_02] da neka pomije bliži.

1754
01:01:55,559 --> 01:01:57,559
[UNKNOWN] A to je služaj.

1755
01:01:57,559 --> 01:02:00,559
[SPEAKER_02] A to je koji bi Isus očiniti.

1756
01:02:00,559 --> 01:02:03,559
[SPEAKER_02] I biti otvoren zato da ti Bog...

1757
01:02:03,559 --> 01:02:04,559
[SPEAKER_02] To je sprava slobodno.

1758
01:02:04,559 --> 01:02:10,559
[SPEAKER_02] Biti otvoren zato da ti Bog snije svakog časa što mu od hoće i gdje od koji ćete staviti poslati.

1759
01:02:10,559 --> 01:02:16,559
[SPEAKER_02] Biti otvoren zato da će biti posljedni na što ne navjeza.

1760
01:02:16,559 --> 01:02:18,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ignačijski duhovni mirno.

1761
01:02:18,559 --> 01:02:21,559
[SPEAKER_02] Mi smo, da će biti ušest, je li tako?

1762
01:02:21,559 --> 01:02:24,559
[SPEAKER_02] Još ima 20 minuta.

1763
01:02:24,559 --> 01:02:27,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ali, vidite će okoliko je sad ovo mi ne iće.

1764
01:02:27,559 --> 01:02:28,559
[SPEAKER_02] Neće biti u nešto.

1765
01:02:28,559 --> 01:02:30,559
[SPEAKER_02] Boreću brzo, rošloda neće.

1766
01:02:30,559 --> 01:02:35,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ti sam sebi ti rastretiti.

1767
01:02:35,559 --> 01:02:40,559
[SPEAKER_02] Sve tih nazija govori nešto što se zove ne navjeza.

1768
01:02:40,559 --> 01:02:47,559
[SPEAKER_02] To je stavljenje u kojem sam spreman što god gdje da je ishod u mojemu životu.

1769
01:02:47,559 --> 01:02:57,559
[SPEAKER_02] I zapravo mi na neki način izabiremo Božji put i idemo za Bogom i živimo sakramentalno.

1770
01:02:57,559 --> 01:03:02,559
[SPEAKER_02] I zapravo nekako u jednom času obrađeni svi to postajemo.

1771
01:03:02,559 --> 01:03:04,559
[SPEAKER_02] Svi postajemo slobodni.

1772
01:03:04,559 --> 01:03:07,559
[SPEAKER_02] Svi dajemo u času kad se davimo.

1773
01:03:07,559 --> 01:03:10,559
[SPEAKER_02] U davit ćemo se, potronit ćemo u more.

1774
01:03:10,559 --> 01:03:13,559
[SPEAKER_02] Mi smo spremljeni na sve.

1775
01:03:13,559 --> 01:03:19,559
[SPEAKER_02] Kada Bog izvuče, osušimo se, operimo, najedemo se, obučemo se.

1776
01:03:19,559 --> 01:03:22,559
[SPEAKER_02] Nis paš više sad spremljeni na sve.

1777
01:03:22,559 --> 01:03:25,559
[SPEAKER_02] Upoznaš svoju ženu, svojeg muža.

1778
01:03:25,559 --> 01:03:28,559
[SPEAKER_02] Dobioš dobar posao, dobioš dobar statusu zajednji.

1779
01:03:28,559 --> 01:03:31,559
[SPEAKER_02] Postaneš sakristal u crkvi.

1780
01:03:31,559 --> 01:03:33,559
[SPEAKER_02] Sad više nisi indiferent.

1781
01:03:36,559 --> 01:03:40,559
[SPEAKER_02] Kad nekako ta slika služenja, glavno služenja, često...

1782
01:03:40,559 --> 01:03:42,559
[SPEAKER_02] A zapravo ipak osješ prazninu.

1783
01:03:42,559 --> 01:03:47,559
[SPEAKER_02] Često vrlo, često ti se dogodi do osješnjaku prazninu.

1784
01:03:47,559 --> 01:03:49,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ja se sjećam kad sam se vratio s Filipina.

1785
01:03:49,559 --> 01:03:51,559
[SPEAKER_02] Najprije ovo, dakle, kad se odšlo,

1786
01:03:51,559 --> 01:03:53,559
[SPEAKER_02] dakle imao sam tu prazninu, najprije,

1787
01:03:53,559 --> 01:03:56,559
[SPEAKER_02] jedan način, obratio sam se,

1788
01:03:56,559 --> 01:03:58,559
[SPEAKER_02] idem komisiji,

1789
01:03:58,559 --> 01:04:00,559
[SPEAKER_02] ne znaš uđu sa sobom.

1790
01:04:00,559 --> 01:04:02,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ništa me ne izgleda.

1791
01:04:02,559 --> 01:04:04,559
[SPEAKER_02] Pa onda bio sam...

1792
01:04:04,559 --> 01:04:07,559
[SPEAKER_02] Sjeto sam bio sam u tom lješkom ratu

1793
01:04:07,559 --> 01:04:08,559
[SPEAKER_02] i postao sam vojnik.

1794
01:04:08,559 --> 01:04:10,559
[SPEAKER_02] Jau, to je to.

1795
01:04:10,559 --> 01:04:12,559
[SPEAKER_02] Pa kako nisam znava?

1796
01:04:12,559 --> 01:04:14,559
[SPEAKER_02] Pa to je ono što ja želim.

1797
01:04:14,559 --> 01:04:17,559
[SPEAKER_02] Služiti da bolim kao vojnik.

1798
01:04:17,559 --> 01:04:19,559
[SPEAKER_02] Pa nema ništa lijepše od toga.

1799
01:04:19,559 --> 01:04:20,559
[SPEAKER_02] Gotovo je.

1800
01:04:20,559 --> 01:04:22,559
[SPEAKER_02] To će biti do kraja životu.

1801
01:04:22,559 --> 01:04:23,559
[SPEAKER_02] A ja sam to...

1802
01:04:23,559 --> 01:04:25,559
[SPEAKER_02] Vidim miliona analogija.

1803
01:04:25,559 --> 01:04:27,559
[SPEAKER_02] Kad bi ljudi kažli...

1804
01:04:27,559 --> 01:04:31,559
[SPEAKER_02] Kada bio sam predpresvetin

1805
01:04:31,559 --> 01:04:33,559
[SPEAKER_02] i Bog mi je pregovorio,

1806
01:04:33,559 --> 01:04:35,559
[SPEAKER_02] sad javno to križam.

1807
01:04:35,559 --> 01:04:37,559
[SPEAKER_02] Koliko god da ste to dogodili?

1808
01:04:37,559 --> 01:04:39,559
[SPEAKER_02] Jau, ti si daleko od spoznanja

1809
01:04:39,559 --> 01:04:41,559
[SPEAKER_02] što je volja Božja.

1810
01:04:41,559 --> 01:04:43,559
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, ja sam...

1811
01:04:43,559 --> 01:04:45,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ljuboj, pa to je, to je.

1812
01:04:45,559 --> 01:04:47,559
[SPEAKER_02] Služi Hrvatskom narodom.

1813
01:04:47,559 --> 01:04:49,559
[SPEAKER_02] Uješ po drugu.

1814
01:04:49,559 --> 01:04:50,559
[SPEAKER_02] Završi.

1815
01:04:50,559 --> 01:04:51,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ide rad krak.

1816
01:04:51,559 --> 01:04:52,559
[SPEAKER_02] Završava rad.

1817
01:04:52,559 --> 01:04:53,559
[SPEAKER_02] Gotov.

1818
01:04:53,559 --> 01:04:55,559
[SPEAKER_02] Praznina, pa kak.

1819
01:04:55,559 --> 01:04:57,559
[SPEAKER_02] Šta ću sad nati u životu?

1820
01:04:57,559 --> 01:04:58,559
[SPEAKER_02] Rad gotov.

1821
01:04:58,559 --> 01:04:59,559
[SPEAKER_02] Kad ću gastu čizvama vojavna,

1822
01:04:59,559 --> 01:05:00,559
[SPEAKER_02] nazad vojavna,

1823
01:05:00,559 --> 01:05:02,559
[SPEAKER_02] ma, lješića.

1824
01:05:02,559 --> 01:05:03,559
[SPEAKER_02] Skidno se.

1825
01:05:03,559 --> 01:05:05,559
[SPEAKER_02] Kad ću sad otvoriti

1826
01:05:05,559 --> 01:05:07,559
[SPEAKER_02] ova zapoznanca uopćini,

1827
01:05:07,559 --> 01:05:08,559
[SPEAKER_02] šef urbanizma,

1828
01:05:08,559 --> 01:05:10,559
[SPEAKER_02] oblikovati grad.

1829
01:05:10,559 --> 01:05:12,559
[SPEAKER_02] Uleđivati parkove, ulice.

1830
01:05:12,559 --> 01:05:14,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ma to je to.

1831
01:05:14,559 --> 01:05:15,559
[SPEAKER_02] Tri godine.

1832
01:05:15,559 --> 01:05:16,559
[SPEAKER_02] Nakon to.

1833
01:05:16,559 --> 01:05:17,559
[SPEAKER_02] Nemo to ga ništa.

1834
01:05:17,559 --> 01:05:18,559
[SPEAKER_02] Gotov.

1835
01:05:18,559 --> 01:05:19,559
[SPEAKER_02] Gotov je zajedno s jedno vrijeme.

1836
01:05:19,559 --> 01:05:22,559
[SPEAKER_02] Otvorim projekti Biro jedno vrijeme.

1837
01:05:22,559 --> 01:05:24,559
[SPEAKER_02] Čijim se otvori šansa,

1838
01:05:24,559 --> 01:05:26,559
[SPEAKER_02] što ću se naprećen dobar plan

1839
01:05:26,559 --> 01:05:28,559
[SPEAKER_02] da ću stekiti profesorima s arhitekture,

1840
01:05:28,559 --> 01:05:30,559
[SPEAKER_02] otvoriti projekti Biro u Posušnju,

1841
01:05:30,559 --> 01:05:32,559
[SPEAKER_02] u urbanistički zapravo zavod,

1842
01:05:32,559 --> 01:05:36,559
[SPEAKER_02] gdje ćemo vi u Hrce-Bosni prodavati,

1843
01:05:36,559 --> 01:05:38,559
[SPEAKER_02] biće lobe do krova.

1844
01:05:38,559 --> 01:05:40,559
[SPEAKER_02] Oduševili ste, oni ko će doli doći,

1845
01:05:40,559 --> 01:05:43,559
[SPEAKER_02] nijela je Hrcegovi gledala kao Eldorado.

1846
01:05:43,559 --> 01:05:46,559
[UNKNOWN] Mašta ti, nema gole.

1847
01:05:46,559 --> 01:05:49,559
[SPEAKER_02] Nih to mu je praznila opet.

1848
01:05:49,559 --> 01:05:52,559
[SPEAKER_02] I na koncu događa se to da ću da idem u sveće

1849
01:05:52,559 --> 01:05:54,559
[SPEAKER_02] i molim ja, molim, u papim,

1850
01:05:54,559 --> 01:05:57,559
[SPEAKER_02] zatim, bio tu u Međugorji pod hladan za zapreća

1851
01:05:57,559 --> 01:05:59,559
[SPEAKER_02] i naglao mene.

1852
01:05:59,559 --> 01:06:01,559
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, neću sa detaljim pričati.

1853
01:06:01,559 --> 01:06:05,559
[SPEAKER_02] I ja odreći moliti da vidim što je, što trebam dalje činiti,

1854
01:06:05,559 --> 01:06:07,559
[SPEAKER_02] put ići dalje u životu

1855
01:06:07,559 --> 01:06:09,559
[SPEAKER_02] i u jednom času bi se zapjesne

1856
01:06:09,559 --> 01:06:11,559
[SPEAKER_02] zapravo svećeniški prozir.

1857
01:06:11,559 --> 01:06:14,559
[SPEAKER_02] Takva na milost obusne.

1858
01:06:14,559 --> 01:06:16,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ne je li ja to?

1859
01:06:16,559 --> 01:06:18,559
[SPEAKER_02] Nikad mi takva radost ne ispona.

1860
01:06:18,559 --> 01:06:19,559
[SPEAKER_02] To je to.

1861
01:06:19,559 --> 01:06:21,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ja ću biti svećeni Hristo.

1862
01:06:21,559 --> 01:06:22,559
[SPEAKER_02] Do ispona.

1863
01:06:22,559 --> 01:06:23,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ja postaram svećeni.

1864
01:06:23,559 --> 01:06:26,559
[SPEAKER_02] Radim ispona što sladim u Zagrebu.

1865
01:06:26,559 --> 01:06:28,559
[SPEAKER_02] Jedno vrijeme.

1866
01:06:28,559 --> 01:06:30,559
[SPEAKER_02] Služim družbi Isusovom.

1867
01:06:30,559 --> 01:06:32,559
[SPEAKER_02] Crkve služim.

1868
01:06:32,559 --> 01:06:34,559
[SPEAKER_02] Daj vam se šta prigovoriti.

1869
01:06:34,559 --> 01:06:36,559
[SPEAKER_02] Otišao na Filipine.

1870
01:06:36,559 --> 01:06:38,559
[SPEAKER_02] Tamo malo vidim, malo zagačim svijet,

1871
01:06:38,559 --> 01:06:39,559
[SPEAKER_02] malo bio iso u Kanadi.

1872
01:06:39,559 --> 01:06:40,559
[SPEAKER_02] Vracam se u Hrvatsku.

1873
01:06:40,559 --> 01:06:41,559
[SPEAKER_02] Dobijem zadatak.

1874
01:06:41,559 --> 01:06:43,559
[SPEAKER_02] Dobijem što trebalo raditi.

1875
01:06:43,559 --> 01:06:46,559
[SPEAKER_02] I onda što mi se događa sada?

1876
01:06:46,559 --> 01:06:49,559
[SPEAKER_02] Vjerovali mi ne.

1877
01:06:49,559 --> 01:06:51,559
[SPEAKER_02] prazadina.

1878
01:06:51,559 --> 01:06:53,559
[UNKNOWN] Opet prazadina.

1879
01:06:53,559 --> 01:06:58,559
[SPEAKER_02] Zašto?

1880
01:06:58,559 --> 01:07:00,559
[SPEAKER_02] I mučilo se to par godina.

1881
01:07:00,559 --> 01:07:02,559
[SPEAKER_02] I ja ne znam što ću.

1882
01:07:02,559 --> 01:07:04,559
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, ja mogu sada reći.

1883
01:07:04,559 --> 01:07:06,559
[SPEAKER_02] Baš me briga.

1884
01:07:06,559 --> 01:07:07,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sam reka pročijal.

1885
01:07:07,559 --> 01:07:08,559
[SPEAKER_02] Evo što treba reći.

1886
01:07:08,559 --> 01:07:09,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ja ću raditi.

1887
01:07:09,559 --> 01:07:11,559
[SPEAKER_02] Odmladimo se u očijeku.

1888
01:07:11,559 --> 01:07:13,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ne znam, vojnika pera.

1889
01:07:13,559 --> 01:07:15,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sam spreman to.

1890
01:07:15,559 --> 01:07:16,559
[SPEAKER_02] I doista nema ništa.

1891
01:07:16,559 --> 01:07:18,559
[SPEAKER_02] Gdje god me stavim masu.

1892
01:07:18,559 --> 01:07:19,559
[SPEAKER_02] Znam, vojnika.

1893
01:07:19,559 --> 01:07:21,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ali ja sam zapravo što je.

1894
01:07:21,559 --> 01:07:23,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sam prebacio odgovornost

1895
01:07:23,559 --> 01:07:25,559
[SPEAKER_02] za vlastniku život.

1896
01:07:25,559 --> 01:07:26,559
[SPEAKER_02] Na projekcijali.

1897
01:07:26,559 --> 01:07:28,559
[SPEAKER_02] A to nije vjero.

1898
01:07:28,559 --> 01:07:30,559
[SPEAKER_02] Nebo ja moram doći.

1899
01:07:30,559 --> 01:07:31,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ponovno se opratiti.

1900
01:07:31,559 --> 01:07:33,559
[SPEAKER_02] Moram ponovno doći pred Hrista.

1901
01:07:33,559 --> 01:07:35,559
[SPEAKER_02] I postaviti pitanje.

1902
01:07:35,559 --> 01:07:36,559
[SPEAKER_02] A razlučivati.

1903
01:07:36,559 --> 01:07:38,559
[SPEAKER_02] Gdje mi trebaš razvoziti.

1904
01:07:38,559 --> 01:07:42,559
[SPEAKER_02] Da ponovno mučio tu nenabezanost.

1905
01:07:42,559 --> 01:07:43,559
[SPEAKER_02] I propitivati.

1906
01:07:43,559 --> 01:07:49,559
[SPEAKER_02] Gdje vati Isus u ovom svijetu danas najviše.

1907
01:07:49,559 --> 01:07:51,559
[SPEAKER_02] Koji je to prostor?

1908
01:07:51,559 --> 01:07:53,559
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, ja sam ipak umadruvoljno za to.

1909
01:07:53,559 --> 01:07:56,559
[SPEAKER_02] I dok nisam to tako na svijetu

1910
01:07:56,559 --> 01:07:57,559
[SPEAKER_02] razmišljao.

1911
01:07:57,559 --> 01:07:58,559
[SPEAKER_02] Bolio se razmišljao.

1912
01:07:58,559 --> 01:07:59,559
[SPEAKER_02] Mučilo me to.

1913
01:07:59,559 --> 01:08:00,559
[SPEAKER_02] Da sam končil.

1914
01:08:00,559 --> 01:08:01,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ja napuš sam shvatio.

1915
01:08:01,559 --> 01:08:02,559
[SPEAKER_02] Što je to?

1916
01:08:02,559 --> 01:08:06,559
[SPEAKER_02] I dok to sam ispunicila u provincijalu.

1917
01:08:06,559 --> 01:08:10,559
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, ja sam na taj način morao ponovno doći

1918
01:08:10,559 --> 01:08:12,559
[SPEAKER_02] i pitati Boga gdje me trebaš.

1919
01:08:12,559 --> 01:08:13,559
[SPEAKER_02] Gdje me trebaš.

1920
01:08:13,559 --> 01:08:16,560
[SPEAKER_02] Nisam samo dovoljno da nisam ja ugrijel.

1921
01:08:16,560 --> 01:08:20,560
[SPEAKER_02] Nisam dovoljno samo to da sam se ja spasio od tonuća

1922
01:08:20,560 --> 01:08:22,560
[SPEAKER_02] ili propasti.

1923
01:08:22,560 --> 01:08:26,560
[SPEAKER_02] Nego punina odnosa među mene i Boga

1924
01:08:26,560 --> 01:08:30,560
[SPEAKER_02] je onda kad sam ja ugrijel spremam služiti.

1925
01:08:30,560 --> 01:08:34,560
[SPEAKER_02] da se pravo uvijek mora povraćati.

1926
01:08:34,560 --> 01:08:38,560
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, vraćanje što stavljamo pred nama stoji kao izrazoga

1927
01:08:38,560 --> 01:08:42,560
[SPEAKER_02] i zapravo kad se ovdje stvari tako više

1928
01:08:42,560 --> 01:08:44,560
[SPEAKER_02] počnemo tako shvatati ovdje

1929
01:08:44,560 --> 01:08:46,560
[SPEAKER_02] i u našoj odnosno pred na crkvi

1930
01:08:46,560 --> 01:08:48,560
[SPEAKER_02] i odnosno pred na Hrvatskoj

1931
01:08:48,560 --> 01:08:53,560
[SPEAKER_02] onda će se i naša domovina obroviti.

1932
01:08:53,560 --> 01:08:56,560
[SPEAKER_02] Nije dovoljno sam se jako sretio.

1933
01:08:56,560 --> 01:08:57,560
[SPEAKER_02] Što je svojim narodom?

1934
01:08:57,560 --> 01:08:58,560
[SPEAKER_02] Što je svojnom domovinom?

1935
01:08:58,560 --> 01:09:00,560
[SPEAKER_02] kako mogu u tome sudirati?

1936
01:09:00,560 --> 01:09:02,560
[SPEAKER_02] A to nije samo propovjedanje.

1937
01:09:02,560 --> 01:09:04,560
[SPEAKER_02] To možda čak i najvakše

1938
01:09:04,560 --> 01:09:06,560
[SPEAKER_02] njegove to služi.

1939
01:09:06,560 --> 01:09:08,560
[SPEAKER_02] To spremio, njegove služi.

1940
01:09:08,560 --> 01:09:18,560
[SPEAKER_02] Pijesma, ali ćemo sad promoliti,

1941
01:09:18,560 --> 01:09:20,560
[SPEAKER_02] da malo to provučamo hodno srce.

1942
01:09:20,560 --> 01:09:24,560
[SPEAKER_02] Da provučemo to srce u stvari,

1943
01:09:24,560 --> 01:09:26,560
[SPEAKER_02] da shvatimo kape nekako.

1944
01:09:26,560 --> 01:09:28,560
[SPEAKER_02] To je jedini problem život.

1945
01:09:28,560 --> 01:09:30,560
[SPEAKER_02] onaj koji je shvatio da je Govinovu daro na ovu život

1946
01:09:30,560 --> 01:09:32,560
[SPEAKER_02] i da sada taj može što hoće,

1947
01:09:32,560 --> 01:09:36,560
[SPEAKER_02] a Gova zove ponekad kad mu zagusti,

1948
01:09:36,560 --> 01:09:38,560
[SPEAKER_02] da je daleko od toga da shvatio život.

1949
01:09:38,560 --> 01:09:40,560
[SPEAKER_02] I taj uvek na putu propasti,

1950
01:09:40,560 --> 01:09:42,560
[SPEAKER_02] na putu da sve izgubi,

1951
01:09:42,560 --> 01:09:44,560
[SPEAKER_02] na putu da sve prokaca,

1952
01:09:44,560 --> 01:09:46,560
[SPEAKER_02] u pravi život,

1953
01:09:46,560 --> 01:09:50,560
[SPEAKER_02] prave dologa sprava.

1954
01:09:50,560 --> 01:09:54,560
[SPEAKER_02] Bogostvoritelj je to da ja vraćam svoj život,

1955
01:09:54,560 --> 01:09:56,560
[SPEAKER_02] a da pravo

1956
01:09:56,560 --> 01:09:58,560
[SPEAKER_02] radost života

1957
01:09:58,560 --> 01:10:00,560
[SPEAKER_02] je u tome da Bogu

1958
01:10:00,560 --> 01:10:02,560
[SPEAKER_02] davio svoj život.

1959
01:10:02,560 --> 01:10:04,560
[SPEAKER_02] Da ste mi dođu takvu slobodu,

1960
01:10:04,560 --> 01:10:06,560
[SPEAKER_02] da najdemu takvu relačiju,

1961
01:10:06,560 --> 01:10:08,560
[SPEAKER_02] takvu slobodu,

1962
01:10:08,560 --> 01:10:10,560
[SPEAKER_02] da Bog uvijek davio sve

1963
01:10:10,560 --> 01:10:12,560
[SPEAKER_02] i da Bog smije sa mnom sve.

1964
01:10:12,560 --> 01:10:14,560
[SPEAKER_02] To je slovo.

1965
01:10:14,560 --> 01:10:16,560
[SPEAKER_02] Onaj ko to, ko nema takav,

1966
01:10:16,560 --> 01:10:17,560
[SPEAKER_02] odnosi takav stav,

1967
01:10:17,560 --> 01:10:19,560
[SPEAKER_02] da prošljuje u strahu.

1968
01:10:19,560 --> 01:10:21,560
[SPEAKER_02] Još živi onaj stariji sin,

1969
01:10:21,560 --> 01:10:23,560
[SPEAKER_02] još živi u najavništu,

1970
01:10:23,560 --> 01:10:25,560
[SPEAKER_02] pred da je upodnomilo od Božju,

1971
01:10:25,560 --> 01:10:26,560
[SPEAKER_02] a stupeti kao sveo,

1972
01:10:26,560 --> 01:10:28,560
[SPEAKER_02] na status najavnika.

1973
01:10:28,560 --> 01:10:30,560
[SPEAKER_02] To ne želim pripada.

1974
01:10:30,560 --> 01:10:32,560
[SPEAKER_02] Imati slobodu,

1975
01:10:32,560 --> 01:10:36,560
[SPEAKER_02] da Bogu uvijek sebi dajem sebe,

1976
01:10:36,560 --> 01:10:38,560
[SPEAKER_02] da Bogu dajem sebe,

1977
01:10:38,560 --> 01:10:40,560
[SPEAKER_02] da smije sa mnom što god voće,

1978
01:10:40,560 --> 01:10:42,560
[SPEAKER_02] napravo u mom srcu,

1979
01:10:42,560 --> 01:10:44,560
[SPEAKER_02] razpiruje takvu radost.

1980
01:10:44,560 --> 01:10:49,560
[SPEAKER_02] I u meni se događa takva emocija ljubavi.

1981
01:10:49,560 --> 01:10:52,560
[SPEAKER_02] Ja ne mogu reći Bogu da ga ljubim,

